STATE

Kenneth Wayne GOFORTH. No. 389P05-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 17, 2006. Anne M. Middleton, Assistant Attorney General, Roxann Vaneekhoven, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 17th day of July 2006 by Defendant for "Notice of Appeal":
